Download logo On January 8, 2022, President Xi Jinping sent a message of sympathy to Mauritanian President Mohamed Ould Ghazouani over his infection with COVID-19.  Xi Jinping said, learning that President Ghazouani is infected with COVID-19, I would like to extend my sympathy to you and wish you a speedy recovery. The Chinese government and the Chinese people firmly support the Mauritanian government and people in fighting the pandemic. I believe that under the leadership of President Ghazouani, Mauritania will surely defeat the pandemic at an early date. Distributed by APO Group on behalf of Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the People’s Republic of China.